Body: What We've Learned Updated: The customer asked if the reboot of the computers is mandatory after the client update.

Next Steps Updated: Because of the Network extension the reboot is mandatory. But after the agent from 5.9.4.1 will be installed the reboot should not be mandatory anymore.
The customers will update the server to 5.9.4.1 and test this.
